{"tid":1745952,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【招人】香港毒氣APPS籌備中！（再POST）","createTime":"2019-11-22T13:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T14:31:53.000Z","uid":341080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00a30adeca47f8efca7e863c9d92c4fdeff6edfc","tid":1745952,"uid":341080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"各位師兄好，我第一次玩連登，請多多指教！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人廢青一名，上星期學校停課冇工開，所以就整理咗催淚彈發射資料，前幾日請槍放上連登，至今已經有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">十三萬</span></span>點擊率。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊post: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1729176\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1729176</a><br />\n附地圖：<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok&amp;ll=22.382581894986814%2C114.10570435&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fembed%3Fmid%3D1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok%26ll%3D22.382581894986814%252C114.10570435%26z%3D11&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=46248029\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok&amp;ll=22.382581894986814%2C114.10570435&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n入正題先，因為資料一路加，google map不勝負荷，會越來越慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以同另一位催淚彈地圖製作人商討會把所有data整成apps!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外會加上<strong>風向對區域影響</strong>，<strong>二噁英指數</strong>，<strong>集合有關催淚彈禍害的文宣</strong> (<span style=\"color: green;\">大家有咩意見可以補充</span>)。<br />\n<br />\n暫時團隊中有化學家，地理學家....但我地仲需要各位大大幫手！￼所以，現在希望招人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">-文宣隊！非常重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-寫apps隊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-各方面的專家！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位有興趣人士都可以pm tg @woohooha <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大家幫我大大力推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />十萬火急，趕住要人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3738bd026b2424ae2f89e84f17530e2b4b148b11","tid":1745952,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23e0527009642796320809b7cad235d121c23698","tid":1745952,"uid":341080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"今日已經二十五萬點擊率，證明大家係需要架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dbd73f41e2eeb46655c3365bdece1c21f5ea92","tid":1745952,"uid":70121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de590e81fc988b0d14ffc74f29454455b65fb10b","tid":1745952,"uid":194255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31cd006b4b3196e501cb2a1a748d9937705bc664","tid":1745952,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"apps名係咪叫毒氣丸，定係叫毒氣雙子"},{"pid":"e8b352574cb4abd6e3e0e5f108d7156c270543f2","tid":1745952,"uid":341080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31cd006b4b3196e501cb2a1a748d9937705bc664","tid":1745952,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"ap